OL,3,CShoplifting offences in England and
OL,4,CWales hit a 20-year high
OL,6,FHome Secretary Yvette Cooper promises
OL,7,Fto put more police on streets,
OL,8,Femphasising the need for people "to
OL,9,Ffeel safe on the streets", as ITV News
OL,10,Freporter Sam Holder reports
OL,12,FThe number of police-recorded
OL,13,Fshoplifting offences have hit a 20-
OL,14,Fyear high across England and Wales.
OL,16,FPolice forces logged a total of
OL,17,F443,995 instances in the year up to
OL,18,FMarch 2024. That is up 30% on the year
OL,19,Fprevious, from 342,428.
