OL,3,CShoplifting offences in England and
OL,4,CWales hit a 20-year high
OL,6,FThe figure is at its highest level
OL,7,Fsince current records began in March
OL,8,F2003, according to the Office for
OL,9,FNational Statistics (ONS), which
OL,10,Fdescribed the latest increases as
OL,11,F"notable".
OL,13,FRetailers have been increasingly
OL,14,Fconcerned about the rising cost of
OL,15,Ftheft. Figures earlier this year
OL,16,Fshowed shoplifting was already at a 20-
OL,17,Fyear high, the latest figures show
OL,18,Fthat it has risen further.
OL,20,FShoplifters wielding machetes target a
OL,21,FCo-op store in Yorkshire last year
