OL,3,CShoplifting offences in England and
OL,4,CWales hit a 20-year high
OL,6,FIn the wake of growing crime
OL,7,Fstatistics, the new Labour government
OL,8,Fhas vowed to tackle low-level
OL,9,Fshoplifting and make assaulting a shop
OL,10,Fworker a specific criminal offence.
OL,12,FThe move follows a long-running bid
OL,13,Ffrom business owners and Tory
OL,14,Fbackbencher Matt Vickers amid rising
OL,15,Fviolence against retail workers.
OL,17,FRetailers hope the measures set out
OL,18,Flast week in the King's Speech to
OL,19,FParliament will make it easier for
OL,20,Fpolice to investigate and prosecute
OL,21,Fcriminals.
