OL,3,CShoplifting offences in England and
OL,4,CWales hit a 20-year high
OL,6,FThe figures also show the number of
OL,7,Foffences involving theft from the
OL,8,Fperson stood at 131,453 in 2023/24, up
OL,9,F17% from 112,225 in 2022/23.
OL,11,FThe number of robberies recorded rose
OL,12,Fby 8% to 81,019, up from 75,012 in the
OL,13,Fprevious 12 months ` though this
OL,14,Fremains below pre-pandemic levels,
OL,15,Fwith 90,198 offences in the year to
OL,16,FMarch 2020.
