OL,3,CShoplifting offences in England and
OL,4,CWales hit a 20-year high
OL,6,FThere was a "notable increase" in the
OL,7,Fnumber of robberies involving a knife
OL,8,For sharp instrument, with 21,226
OL,9,Frecorded by forces in 2023/24, up 13%
OL,10,Ffrom 18,787 in the previous 12 months,
OL,11,Fthough this is below the 22,727 in
OL,12,F2019/20.
OL,14,FOffences involving possession of an
OL,15,Farticle with a blade or point fell
OL,16,Fslightly to 27,470, down 3% from
OL,17,F28,391 in the previous 12 months.
