OL,3,CShoplifting offences in England and
OL,4,CWales hit a 20-year high
OL,6,FThis follows "substantial increases in
OL,7,Frecent years, which may have been
OL,8,Finfluenced by targeted police action
OL,9,Fto tackle knife crime", the ONS said.
OL,11,FHome Secretary Yvette Cooper said the
OL,12,Ffigures represent "the appalling
OL,13,Flegacy of the Conservative government
OL,14,Fon law and order".
OL,16,FShe added: "We have soaring
OL,17,Fshoplifting and soaring street crime
OL,18,Fhappening at a time when we have
OL,19,Fplummeting neighbourhood police."
